ED_DecisionText:
At its 68th plenary meeting, on 23 December 2016, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the Fifth Committee,  took note of the report of the Secretary-General on the United Nations Office for Partnerships. 

(See A/71/716, para. 53,  A/71/PV.68)
ED_Disclaimer: The text of this decision is available in all languages in document A/71/49 (Vol. II).
